abstract: Western Global Airlines, corporate owner of cargo jet impounded in Zimbabwe after man's bloody corpse was found on board, confirm man was stowaway with no connection to company or specific cargo shipment.
lead_paragraph: The American corporate owner of the cargo jet impounded in Zimbabwe after the bloodied body of a man was discovered aboard during a refueling stop confirmed that man was a stowaway.

headline.main: Zimbabwe: Owner of Impounded Jet Says Body on Board Was a Stowaway
headline.print_headline: Africa; Zimbabwe: Owner of Impounded Jet Says Body on Board Was a Stowaway
